text: Notuner Gaan (; "The Song of Youth"), more popularly known (after its first line) as Chol Chol Chol is the national march () of Bangladesh., == Lyrics == Bengali Transliteration English translation Here are the rest of the original lyrics from which the National march of Bangladesh came (continuing from the last section): Bengali Transliteration English translation Marching Song Chal Chal ChalMarching Song (Chal Chal Chal) == References == Category:National symbols of Bangladesh Category:Asian anthems
title: Notuner Gaan
